HEADWORD: Tachygraphy
<hw>Ta*chyg"ra*phy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>tachy`s</grk> quick + <ets>-graphy</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>tachygraphie</ets>.]</ety> <def>The art or practice of rapid
writing; shorthand writing; stenography.</def> <rj><au>I. Taylor (The
